The LIVE production site at https://split.lease/404 encountered a redirect loop error (ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS), preventing me from capturing a screenshot for comparison. However, I was able to successfully load and capture the DEV version at http://localhost:8010/404.

The DEV page loads correctly with:
- Full 404 error page layout
- Header navigation with "Host with Us" and "Stay with Us" buttons
- 404 error message with "Go Home" and "Search Listings" CTAs
- Footer with company info, host/guest sections, referral widget, and import listing form
- Mobile app and Alexa promotional sections
- No console errors
